data.description: FINISHED BASEMENT WITH EGRESS WINDOWS!!! Built in 2021, this IMPECCABLE ranch style home has many upgraded features. Captivating open floor plan. Kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and a reverse osmosis system. Eating nook has glass doors to the deck. Washer and dryer are included in the main floor laundry. Master suite is gorgeous with tiled walk in shower, walk in closet, tub and private toilet room. There are 5 bedrooms, 2 of which are in the lower level with a full bath and family room. Smoke/carbon dioxide detectors are hardwired throughout. The spacious driveway provides a basketball court with built in basketball hoop. Always have a pristine lawn with the underground sprinkler system. Make this house your new home!
